abstract: Police in Minneapolis suburb report apparent murder-suicide involving family of five, including three children, all found dead in their upscale lakeside home; names of victims are not released.
lead_paragraph: Three children were among those found dead in an upscale Minneapolis suburb in what police said appeared to be a murder-suicide.

headline.main: Minnesota: Five in Family Found Dead in Home
